reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to use
reviews.reviewText: This product is perfect to use on the outside of a do it yourself first aid kit. These are peel and stick and I used them on a lidded plastic see through box for a boating first aid kit. When not on the boat it's in the linen closet and is easy to find with the stickers on all four side. The large size stickers are easily seen.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 5, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars 4 first aid decals many application's
reviews.reviewText: So you get four decals per your order, if ur like me and enjoy putting labels on kits this item is for you. I purchased a wallet years ago from a large clothing branch and it came in a metal box. I've since enjiyed building my edc kits so i kept that box for years. Now I'm putting together a first aid kit and it was already a red box so i really needed a 1st aid decal and this one fit the bill. It was the percect size. I was going to round the sides off because of my ocd but I can live with the straight corners. Decal feels well made, I'm a large format digital printer tech and the substrate/plastic film is a very well made material. Its a PSA, material meaning it's pressure sensitive adhesive. It's not cheap material i removed it several times before making certain it was perfectly straight. I have no complaints, it worked well for my application and im considering making a few more fisrt aid kits. Would i recommend these yeup, without a doubt. I wasn't provided these decals in turn for my review nor was my item discounted. Hope this helps
